{"tid":2152753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門市廣場要求移除民主女神像 Chickeeduck稱法庭已發臨時禁制令","createTime":"2020-08-12T07:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T07:15:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c72572e73c2f0a6bf88931bb166d7358c59a018","tid":2152753,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2F6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=2af81c30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2F6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE%2F&h=f94a839d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/6SUN7LAJQ4BW4R27YH3ZYK3DOE/</a><br />\n<br />\n連鎖童裝店Chickeeduck早前在荃灣愉景新城分店擺放香港「民主女神像」，遭商場要求移走雕像，業主其後拒絕續租。Chickeeduck早前再在屯門市廣場分店擺放女神像，遭業主入稟高院，指控違反租約，要求法庭頒令強制該店24小時內移走雕像，否則業主有權進場處置。Chickeeduck回覆本報查詢，表示昨晚已收到法庭頒發的臨時禁制令，由於租約的陳列條例模糊，公司現正與法律團隊商討。"},{"pid":"e33db6d1592ee19362d072a46b2b76d61ad2cde5","tid":2152753,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"唔係有個民主像 真係無人會去你個場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3333d44d14fbcb2ac3c585be2cb549a1625cb090","tid":2152753,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"信和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b403df341690ae40f0edac1f1eb27b4d6bb5bc","tid":2152753,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"Ok, 等法庭頒令先囉<br />\n如果輸咗，我係都唔拆，你自己派人硬闖入嚟拆囉<br />\n畫面有咁肉酸得咁肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkg